'''Gray Talon''' was an outlaw organization which was active in the early years of the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], dealing in [[Pirate/Legends|piracy]] as well as [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggling]]. Their central base of operation was the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim]] [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Dantooine/Legends|Dantooine]].

They had a run-in with pirate warlord [[Nym/Legends|Nym]] and looted the abandoned [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] [[Dantooine base/Legends|base]] on Dantooine.

